# textdomain: mcl_doc
Water can flow into this block and cause it to drop as an item.=Voda lahko steče v ta blok in povzroči, da izpade kot predmet.
This block can be turned into dirt with a hoe.=Ta blok se lahko z motiko spremeni v zemljo.
This block can be turned into farmland with a hoe.=Ta blok se lahko z motiko spremeni v njivo.
This block can be turned into grass path with a shovel.=Ta blok se lahko z lopato spremeni v travnato pot.
This block acts as a soil for all saplings.=Ta blok služi kot zemlja za vse sadike.
This block acts as a soil for some saplings.=Ta blok služi kot zemlja za nekatere sadike.
Sugar canes will grow on this block.=Na tem bloku raste sladkorni trs.
Nether wart will grow on this block.=Na tem bloku raste Nether bradavica.

This block quickly decays when there is no wood block of any species within a distance of @1. When decaying, it disappears and may drop one of its regular drops. The block does not decay when the block has been placed by a player.=Ta blok hitro propade, če na razdalji @1 ni nobenega lesenega bloka katere koli vrste. Pri propadanju izgine in lahko izpleni enega od svojih običajnih izplenov. Blok ne propade, če ga je postavil igralec.

This block quickly decays and disappears when there is no wood block of any species within a distance of @1. The block does not decay when the block has been placed by a player.=Ta blok hitro propade in izgine, če na razdalji @1 ni nobenega lesenega bloka katere koli vrste. Blok ne propade, če ga je postavil igralec.

This plant can only grow on grass blocks and dirt. To survive, it needs to have an unobstructed view to the sky above or be exposed to a light level of 8 or higher.=Ta rastlina lahko raste samo na travnatih blokih in zemlji. Za preživetje potrebuje neoviran pogled na nebo nad njo ali pa mora biti izpostavljena stopnji svetlobe 8 ali več.

This plant can grow on grass blocks, podzol, dirt and coarse dirt. To survive, it needs to have an unobstructed view to the sky above or be exposed to a light level of 8 or higher.=Ta rastlina lahko raste na travnatih blokih, podzolu, zemlji in grobi zemlji. Za preživetje potrebuje neoviran pogled na nebo nad njo ali pa mora biti izpostavljena stopnji svetlobe 8 ali več.

This block is flammable.=Ta blok je vnetljiv.
This block destroys any item it touches.=Ta blok uniči vsak predmet, ki se ga dotakne.
To eat it, wield it, then right-click.=Da ga pojeste, ga držite v roki in kliknite z desnim gumbom.
You can eat this even when your hunger bar is full.=To lahko pojeste, tudi ko je vaša vrstica lakote polna.
You cannot eat this when your hunger bar is full.=Tega ne morete pojesti, ko je vaša vrstica lakote polna.
To drink it, wield it, then right-click.=Da ga spijete, ga držite v roki in kliknite z desnim gumbom.
You cannot drink this when your hunger bar is full.=Tega ne morete spiti, ko je vaša vrstica lakote polna.
To consume it, wield it, then right-click.=Da ga zaužijete, ga držite v roki in kliknite z desnim gumbom.
You cannot consume this when your hunger bar is full.=Tega ne morete zaužiti, ko je vaša vrstica lakote polna.
You have to wait for around 2 seconds before you can eat or drink again.=Počakati morate približno 2 sekundi, preden lahko spet jeste ali pijete.
Hunger points restored: @1=Obnovljene točke lakote: @1
Saturation points restored: @1=Obnovljene točke sitosti: @1
It can be worn on the head.=Lahko se nosi na glavi.
It can be worn on the torso.=Lahko se nosi na trupu.
It can be worn on the legs.=Lahko se nosi na nogah.
It can be worn on the feet.=Lahko se nosi na stopalih.
Armor points: @1=Točke oklepa: @1
Armor durability: @1=Vzdržljivost oklepa: @1
This item can be repaired at an anvil with: @1.=Ta predmet se lahko popravi na nakovalu z: @1.
This item can be repaired at an anvil with any wooden planks.=Ta predmet se lahko popravi na nakovalu s katerimi koli lesenimi deskami.
This item can be repaired at an anvil with any item in the “@1” group.=Ta predmet se lahko popravi na nakovalu s katerim koli predmetom iz skupine »@1«.
This item cannot be renamed at an anvil.=Tega predmeta ni mogoče preimenovati na nakovalu.
This block crushes any block it falls into.=Ta blok zdrobi vsak blok, v katerega pade.

When this block falls deeper than 1 block, it causes damage to any player it hits. The damage dealt is B×2−2 hit points with B @= number of blocks fallen. The damage can never be more than 40 HP.=Ko ta blok pade globlje kot 1 blok, povzroči škodo vsakemu igralcu, ki ga zadene. Povzročena škoda znaša B×2−2 točk zdravja, kjer je B @= število blokov padca. Škoda nikoli ne more biti večja od 40 HP.

